<HEADLINE> World Newspaper Congress Opens in Brazil </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Organized by World Association of Newspapers, both meetings,
which continue until coming Friday, bring together 1,500 press
professionals, who will debate a wide range of matters concerning
printed newspapers, among these, stand out Internet's impact and
new technologies in journalistic activity.
</P>
