<HEADLINE> Iran in New Phase of Ties With Other Countries: Khatami </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, June 12 (Xinhua) -- Iranian President Mohammad Khatami
said here Monday that Iran has entered a new phase of relations
with countries in the region and the world, and will further
consolidate the ties by protecting mutual interests.
</P>
<P>
