Cypriot Minister of Commerce, Industry and Tourism Nicos Rolandis,
the Islamic Republic News Agency reported.
</P>
<P>
Khatami said Cyprus is highly significant to Iran as it links
Asia and Europe, adding that he hopes further expansion of
bilateral relations.
</P>
<P>
The Cypriot minister said his country is also keen on boosting
relations with Iran, especially in the fields of commerce,
transportation, tourism and energy.
</P>
<P>
