talented personnel in China last year, up 2,000 compared to the
previous year.
</P>
<P>
The Shanghai Municipal People's Government gives top priority
to the development of human resources. It has abolished residence
registration for talented personnel, the official said.
</P>
<P>
He also said that some new websites for human resources and an
international human resource market will be established soon.
