<HEADLINE> Leading Bank to Support Western Development: President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
URUMQI, June 12 (Xinhua) -- China's leading commercial bank,
the Industrial and Commercial Bank of China, announced here today
that it will support building infrastructure projects in the
western China.
</P>
<P>
Jiang Jianqing, bank president, said today top priority will be
given to trunk highway projects linking capital cities, and
capital cities with other major cities in the region, major
telecommunications, oil, natural gas and power projects.
</P>
