loan guarantee item, adding the bank will watch closely the
capital needs for large projects in west China such as the natural
gas pipeline between Tarim in the Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region
and Shanghai in east China. Financial consulting will also be
provided for these projects.
</P>
