<HEADLINE> Kuala Lumpur Stocks Close Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, June 12 (Xinhua) -- Share prices on the Kuala
Lumpur Stock Exchange closed lower Monday.
</P>
<P>
At the close, the 100-quality stocks Composite Index lost 2.40
points to 858.90, the all-share Emas Index fell 1.64 points to 215.
15, the Industrial Index dropped 1.53 points to 1,510.97 and the
Second Board Index shed 3.60 points to 223.07.
</P>
<P>
Losers led gainers by 546 to 124 while 102 counters were
unchanged and 206 others untraded.
</P>
