costs and benefits of renting mobile diesel generators to produce
180 megawatts of electricity in a bid to reduce the supply deficit
of 400 megawatts in the country.
</P>
<P>
The ongoing power rationing, starting from last September and
worsening in June this year, has hampered the industry sector
greatly and undermined the investment confidence in the country.
