<HEADLINE> Chinese President Greets Russian National Day </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 12 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin
Monday hailed the establishment and development of the strategic
and cooperative partnership between China and Russia as a correct
historic choice.
</P>
<P>
In a message sent to his Russian counterpart Vladimir Putin on
Russia's National Day which falls on Monday, Jiang said that
building and developing such a partnership between the two
neighbors is "a right historic choice the two peoples have made."
</P>
