occasion of Russia's National Day, Jiang said he would like to
send his best wishes to the Russian people on behalf of the
Chinese government and the people and in his own name.
</P>
<P>
He expressed the belief that under President Putin's leadership,
the hard-working and intelligent Russian people would make great
achievements in making their country even more dynamic. 
