public confidence, realize the importance of the tasks facing the
republic and unconditionally observe the Russian constitution and
federal laws.
</P>
<P>
In a report broadcast by ORT channel Putin said that it is
symbolic that the solution of a burning question for organizing
the government system in Chechnya was found on June 12 - the
national holiday of Russia.
</P>
<P>
Kadyrov, for his turn, expressed his adherence to a peaceful
settlement in Chechnya. "From the first day I tried to prevent (
the war), and now I am trying to stop this war, end it," he said.
</P>
<P>
"An end to the war will be possible only, if gang leaders such
as(field commander Ibn-ul) Khattab, (Shamil) Basayev are no more,"
the Interfax news agency quoted him as saying. 
