food industries, house appliances and textiles cooperatives put
their products on display at the fair.
</P>
<P>
At the 6th international power, electronics and computer
exhibition, 393 Iranian and foreign companies have exhibited a
variety of their products on an area of 19,545 square meters, he
said.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, 177 Iranian firms and 62 foreign ones are taking part
in the 4th international fair of mineral machinery, construction
materials and dimensional stones, which is organized in cooperation
with a German company.
</P>
<P>
The value of exports in the mines and metals sector during last
Iranian calendar year (ended March 19) exceeded 400 million dollars
and is expected to reach 600 million dollars this Iranian year,
Qassemi said.
</P>
<P>
At the 10th chinaware, ceramics and glass trade fair, 166
Iranian firms have put a variety of their products on display in an
area of 14,000 square meters.
</P>
<P>
A total of 900 production, industrial and export companies from
Iran and 100 foreign firms are taking part in the four-day fairs,
he added. 
