<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, June 12 (Xinhua) -- Pakistani Coast Guards (PCG) in
Balochistan province recovered about 100 kilograms of good quality
drug in a raid at Gwadar-Turbat Road on Monday, according to the
Associated Press of Pakistan (APP).
</P>
