<HEADLINE> India to Provide 100 Mln U.S. Dollar Credit to Sri Lanka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
These remarks were made in a joint statement issued here
following External Affairs Minister Jaswant Singh's two-day
official visit to Sri Lanka.
</P>
<P>
Singh held talks with Sri Lankan President Chandrika
Kumaratunga and other Sri Lankan leaders, and emphatically told
them that "India do not want to get involved in any fire fight" to
