<HEADLINE> Capital Market to Spur Development In Western China (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Scholars also suggest that western China should issue financial
commercial bonds and take the lead to issue bonds for
construction of local basic projects.
</P>
<P>
Venture capital investment funds should be established to
support the development of high-tech and new industries in western
China, they added. Funds for the development of western China,
however, cannot be provided solely by the State.
</P>
<P>
"Western development initiatives will be a daydream without
investment, making it an urgent necessity to boost the capital
market," said Wei Houkai, a research fellow from the CASS Western
Development Research Center.
</P>
<P>
People have increased their deposits in recent years and it is
an ideal choice to invest the deposits in the capital market,
economic experts said.
</P>
<P>
Restructuring the economic system will also provide a huge
demand for the surge of the western region capital market.
</P>
<P>
Authorities said that the conditions for a soaring capital
market have already become mature in western China, citing that
the area already has securities and market intermediaries. Western
China can learn from eastern China in developing its capital
market. 
