<HEADLINE> Prices of Gold Down in India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Standard gold fell further by 20 rupees (0.46 U.S. dollar) to
end at 4,480 rupees (104.19 dollars) per 10 grams from 4,500
rupees (104.65 dollars).
</P>
