<HEADLINE> Land Auction in HK Yields HK$344 Mln For Govt Revenue </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 12 (Xinhua) -- Two government lots were sold
for a total of 344 million HK dollars (44.1 million U.S. dollars)
at a public auction held here by the Lands Department of the Hong
Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR) Monday afternoon.
</P>
