U.S. dollars) for an area of 22,973 square meters. The opening bid
was 80 million HK dollars (10.3 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
Market analysts said the results of the auction were almost the
same as expected and the land sales would help maintain a stable
property market. 
