and culture, honor the film artists and promote international
cultural relations, the radio quoted organizers as saying.
</P>
<P>
Rallies and seminars regarding improving Nepalese film industry
will be held on the occasion and even the nominated films will be
shown in movie halls of major cities, according to the organizers.
</P>
<P>
The festival, to be held after a gap of more than two years, is
co-organized by Nepal Motion Picture Association and Nepal Film
Producers' Association. 
