local capacity to improve the country's fisheries sector since
early last year when the EU imposed a ban on Ugandan fish.
</P>
<P>
Fisheries in Uganda have acquired the capacity to meet the EU
standards, said FIRRI Director Richard Ogutu Ohwayo. 
