<HEADLINE> World Bank to Aid Kenya on Energy Crisis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, June 12 (Xinhua) -- A World Bank team will arrive in
Kenya this week to assess a proposal by the east African country
to alleviate the biting shortage of electricity.
</P>
<P>
